      <td>Cloud-hosted relational database, Supabase Auth tokens, and Row-Level Security (RLS) policies.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><strong>Deployment Pipeline</strong></td>
      <td>Vercel Global Edge CDN</td>
      <td>Automated CI/CD integration connected directly to <code>origin/main</code> on GitHub.</td>
    </tr>
